      "passage_index": 13,
      "title": "John Blair Smith Todd",
      "score": 0.040987403148261985,
      "text": "John Blair Smith Todd\nJohn Blair Smith Todd (April 4, 1814 – January 5, 1872) was a Delegate from Dakota Territory to the United States House of Representatives and a general in the Union Army during the American Civil War.",
